Class InlineXBRLGeneratorException

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Throwable
      java.lang.Exception
          com.fujitsu.xml.xbrl.inlinexbrl.generator.InlineXBRLGeneratorException
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class InlineXBRLGeneratorException
extends java.lang.Exception

This class provides error information found while generating inline XBRL documents.

getErrorCode() returns an error code. Users can describe own procedure according to the each error code.
Also, if the reported error is related with a specific mapping, the mapping can be obtained by calling getMapping().
